State Machines
Why three state machines exist
One machine cannot do three morally different jobs without category
confusion.
PoRH exists for deliberate human application (rehabilitation, scaffolding,
restraint under active management). It records protection achieved
through human effort, but it does not claim that nature can now stand on
its own.
PoP exists for withdrawal and exposure. It tests whether ecological
continuity holds when support is removed and stress arrives. PoP is the
gate that makes ecological truth non-forgeable.
PoR exists for directional improvement under uninterrupted Protection. It
refuses “effort as progress” and recognises only net state improvement
that persists across stress intervals.
This separation enforces the core doctrine: money may settle obligation, but
only time under stress settles truth.
Shared architecture across PoP , PoRH, PoR
1) Seasonal endpoints as the clock
All three machines advance only at declared seasonal endpoints
(observational witness via the Boolean Seasonal Gate). This prevents gaming
through calendar timing and enforces comparable system states.
2) Boolean gates, nuance above
At the protocol layer, each season resolves as a Boolean outcome per gate:
PASS or FAIL only.
Nuance, narrative, and diagnostics live above the state machine. This
keeps settlement crisp and contestable.
3) Trias Testium as the truth filter
Each seasonal resolution is adjudicated through three independent, non-
sovereign witness classes:
Observational
Laboratory
Human
Contradiction rule (hard): incompatible Boolean resolution of the same
declared gate across independent witnesses collapses continuity or increases
constraint. Contradiction never selects truth and never rewrites history.
4) BGUs and EVUs are qualification plumbing
BGU: a witnessed interval of ecological time that remained intact under
declared stress and restraint conditions.
EVU: protocol-level verification record that attests successful witnessing of
BGUs.
BGUs accumulate only through uninterrupted continuity. EVUs qualify those
BGUs for state transitions. Neither has meaning outside qualification.
5) EDA and Pressure Class scale burden, not outcomes
Pressure Class and Ecological Difficulty Adjustment increase:
witnessing intensity
audit frequency
obligation requirements
qualification window length
They never soften PASS thresholds.
Machine 1: PoRH State Machine (Protection under Human
Application)
Purpose
PoRH is the lawful place for:
FMNR, Justdiggit-style scaffolding
active restoration and rehabilitation
anti-poaching and boundary enforcement under management
community agriculture cells operating within declared subsistence bounds
(if ex ante declared)
PoRH says: “Humans are holding the line.
”
It does not say: “The ecosystem can now hold the line.
”
States
PoRH.INACTIVE: cell not enrolled in PoRH.
PoRH.ACTIVE: active rehabilitation or applied protection underway.
PoRH.VALIDATED(season): season passed PoRH gates, EVUs minted for the
season.
PoRH.FAIL: season failed or contradiction occurred; continuity resets for
PoRH accounting.
Transition logic (conceptual)
INACTIVE → ACTIVE when the cell declares PoRH plan, roles, methods, and
dependency layers ex ante.
ACTIVE → VALIDATED at seasonal endpoint if PoRH gates PASS under Trias
Testium.
ACTIVE/VALIDATED → FAIL if any gate FAILs or contradiction occurs.
Key doctrine constraints
PoRH can run for years without implying PoP eligibility.
PoRH is where “exogenous engineering” may occur only as transitional
facilitation that can be withdrawn without collapse.
PoRH replaces baselines with responsibility thresholds: you are not
compared to “what once was,” you are compared to what you must now
hold.
Machine 2: PoP State Machine (Protection under Withdrawal
and Stress)
Purpose
PoP is the Withdrawal Test made operational.
PoP asks one thing: did ecological entropy fail to accelerate across declared
stress windows after intervention was withdrawn?
If yes, ecological time remains intact (BGUs accumulate). If no, continuity
collapses.
PoP is therefore the backbone of BDR as ecological memory.
States
PoP .NOT_ELIGIBLE: cell has not satisfied withdrawal prerequisites.
PoP .WITHDRAWAL_PENDING: withdrawal declared but not yet complete or
not yet observed through an endpoint.
PoP .QUAL_WINDOW(k): in the k-th consecutive season of PoP qualification
(BGUs accumulating).
PoP .PASS_LOCKED: minimum consecutive window achieved (PoP-qualified
for BDR advancement gating).
PoP .FAIL: any seasonal failure or contradiction collapses continuity for the
window and resets k.
PoP .OUT
_
OF_SERVICE: disturbance declared (e.g., extraction) suspends
ecological time accounting for the cell.
Transition guards
NOT_ELIGIBLE → WITHDRAWAL_PENDING when withdrawal is declared and
enforceable.
WITHDRAWAL_PENDING → QUAL_WINDOW(1) at first seasonal endpoint
after withdrawal if PoP PASS.
QUAL_WINDOW(k) → QUAL_WINDOW(k+1) if PASS again.
QUAL_WINDOW(k) → FAIL if any FAIL or contradiction.
FAIL → WITHDRAWAL_PENDING or QUAL_WINDOW(1) depending on
whether withdrawal still holds and whether re-entry requirements are met.
ANY → OUT
_
OF_SERVICE when disturbance is declared (Access Bond posted
ex ante if extractive).
OUT
_
OF_SERVICE → WITHDRAWAL_PENDING after rehabilitation and
withdrawal are complete; then requalification begins.
Why PoP must be Boolean
If PoP were scored, averaged, or negotiated, it becomes finance-friendly.
Finance then pressures the score. The system would quietly drift from truth to
narrative. Boolean gates are the simplest defence.
Machine 3: PoR State Machine (Regeneration under
Uninterrupted Protection)
Purpose
PoR recognises only net ecological state improvement that:
1. occurs under uninterrupted PoP , and
2. persists across stress intervals.
PoR is not “activity.” It is not “spend.” It is not “intent.
”
It is directional improvement that reality did not disprove.
States
PoR.LOCKED: cannot even be evaluated unless PoP continuity holds.
PoR.OBSERVING: monitoring improvement criteria across seasons while
PoP continues.
PoR.UPGRADE_ELIGIBLE: sustained directional improvement achieved
across required windows.
PoR.UPGRADED: PoR state transition recorded (this can trigger BDR stage
transition if other guards hold).
PoR.FAIL: either PoP continuity failed (automatic PoR collapse), or
improvement criteria not met (no upgrade, but not necessarily a “failure” if
PoP still holds).
Dependency on PoP
PoR is strictly subordinate:
If PoP collapses, PoR collapses.
If PoP holds but PoR does not improve, you may remain protected without
claiming regeneration.
This prevents “regeneration theatre.
”
How they combine to advance BDR
Think of BDR as a stage machine that listens to PoP and PoR outputs.
BDR states (minimal)
BDR.STAGE_0: no recorded continuity yet.
BDR.STAGE_1..n: increasing ecological maturity and constraint.
BDR.HALT: contradiction or unresolved ambiguity pauses advancement
(time must judge).
Advancement rule (conceptual)
BDR advances only when:
1. PoP has achieved the required consecutive qualification window (BGUs
intact, EVUs present).
2. PoR has achieved the required sustained improvement window for the
target stage, if stage requires regeneration.
3. No contradictions exist under Trias Testium for any declared gate.
4. All declared dependency layers resolve as required (critical failures gate
PoP , important failures block PoR upgrades, observational failures are
recorded only).
Why BDR must not hard-cap per site
BDR issuance tightens asymptotically as integrity rises. Scarcity emerges from
ecological success, not administration. This is why EDA exists.
Design justification in one coherent chain
PoRH allows honest work without pretending it is truth.
PoP forces exposure and makes truth expensive to claim.
PoR allows improvement claims only when protection already holds, and
only when improvement survives stress.
BDR records the accumulated result as ecological memory, indifferent to
markets, and increasingly constrained by maturity through EDA.
Or in the u-Kama idiom: the seasons are not invoices. They are tests.
